         <br>
         <br>
         <strong>Order Check Copies</strong> <br>
         <ul>
            <li>Tap your checking account </li>
            <li>Tap the <strong>I Want To …</strong> tab at the bottom</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>Order Check Copies</strong> and follow the instructions for viewing or ordering check copies</li>
            </ul>
               <div class="or"> Or </div>
            <ul>
            <li>Go to <strong>Help &amp; Support</strong> on the main menu</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>View or Order Check Copies</strong></li>
            <li>Select an account and follow the instructions for viewing or ordering check copies</li>
         </ul>
         <br>
         <br>
         <strong>View Routing and Account Numbers</strong> <br>
         <ul>
            <li>On smartphones, tap your checking or savings account</li>
            <li>Tap the <strong>Details</strong> tab at the bottom</li>
            <li>The account and routing numbers for that account are displayed</li>
            </ul>
               <div class="or"> Or </div>
            <ul>
            <li>On iPads, tap your checking or savings account</li>
            <li>Tap the <strong>arrow</strong> icon next to Available Balance</li>
            <li>Select <strong>Routing Number</strong> or <strong>Account Number</strong> to view the details</li>
         </ul>
         <br>
         <br>
         <strong>Add Nicknames (iPhone and Android)</strong> <br>
         <ul>
            <li>Tap the account you want to nickname</li>
            <li>Tap the <strong>Details</strong> tab at the bottom</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>Add Nickname</strong></li>
            <li>Enter the nickname and tap <strong>Done</strong></li>
            </ul>
               <div class="or"> Or </div>
            <ul>
            <li>Go to <strong>Profile &amp; Settings</strong> on the main menu</li>
            <li>Tap <strong>Account Nicknames</strong></li>
            <li>Select the account to nickname</li>
            <li>Enter the nickname and tap <strong>Done</strong></li>
