•	Any manual adjustment or updated opt-out preference signal will override previous settings
</p></div><div class="ot-desc-cntr ot-hide ot-always-active-group" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" id="ot-desc-id-CADCA"><div class="ot-grp-hdr1"><h4 class="ot-cat-header">Children's Privacy</h4><div class="ot-tgl-cntr"><div class="ot-always-active">Always Active</div></div></div><p class="ot-grp-desc ot-category-desc">Bank of America is committed to protecting children’s privacy and limiting the collection and use of minor’s data.
